<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>L'Ordinateur Tr√®s Bien - Register Form</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon-96x96.png" sizes="96x96" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png" />
    <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest" />
</head>

<body class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center vh-100 bg-white">
    <div class="container shadow rounded parent-container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5 bg-light d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center">
                <div class="w-75 p-4">
                    <h3 class="text-center mb-4 fw-bold fs-4 primary-text">Register</h3>

                    <form action="/register" method="POST">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label primary-text" for="email">Email</label>
                            <input class="form-control primary-text black-text" name="email" type="email" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label primary-text" for="fullName">Full Name</label>
                            <input class="form-control primary-text black-text" name="fullName" type="text" required>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label primary-text" for="address">Shipping Address</label>
                            <input class="form-control primary-text black-text" name="address" type="text" required>
                        </div>

                        <p class="text-end">
                            <a class="text-decoration-none primary-small-text fst-italic" href="#" onclick="generateUsername()">Generate Username?</a>
                        </p>

                        <button class="btn btn-dark w-100 text-white primary-text" type="submit">Register</button>

                    </form>

                    <div class="divider">
                        <span>or</span>
                    </div>

                    <p class="text-center primary-small-text">Already Have an Account? 
                        <a class="text-decoration-none primary-small-text fw-bold fst-italic" href="/login">Login</a>
                    </p>

                    <% if (error) { %>
                        <p class="text-center text-danger primary-small-text"><%= error %></p>
                    <% } %>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-lg-7 p-5">
                <img class="img-fluid mx-auto d-block" src="/images/computer.jpg" alt="Computer Image">
                <h3 class="text-center fw-bold fs-4 primary-text">Bienvenue Folk!</h3>
                <p class="text-center primary-text">Comment ca va? Ta familla ca va? Too many worries for buying a new computer or laptop or other related components is kind of unnecessary. In our shop here, you can find different kinds of what you need, related to computer and laptop, and of course, not a scam! If you transfer the money, we will just block you. We are not a scam! A bientot!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('./partials/flash') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>

    <script src="/js/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>